Title: Anyonic Realization of the Quantum Affine Lie Algebra U_q(A_N)
Authors: L. Frappat and A. Sciarrino and S. Sciuto and P. Sorba
Abstract: We give a realization of quantum affine Lie algebra $U_q(\hat A_{N-1})$ in terms of anyons defined on a two-dimensional lattice, the deformation parameter $q$ being related to the statistical parameter $\nu$ of the anyons by $q = e^{i\pi\nu}$. In the limit of the deformation parameter going to one we recover the Feingold-Frenkel fermionic construction of undeformed affine Lie algebra.
